# File: app/styles/bootstrap-theme.min.css.ab
# Purpose: Bootstrap 3.3.7 theme CSS — minified production copy stored in app/styles/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
Minified copy of the Bootstrap 3.3.7 optional theme CSS (5 lines). The compressed form of `app/styles/bootstrap-theme.css`, providing gradient and shadow enhancements on Bootstrap components.

## Interface
No exports. Loaded as a `<link>` stylesheet in `app/index.html`.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies. Vendor file. Requires `bootstrap.min.css` to be loaded first.

## Implementation Notes
- Bootstrap theme version: 3.3.7
- 5 lines minified
- Identical in content to `app/assets/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css`
